<p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 18px;">经管er</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">翻地挖坑，开掘渠道，播种种子，树立劳动最光荣、劳动最崇高、劳动最伟大、劳动最美丽的观念，一起出力流汗、用自己的双手种下希望的树苗，用劳动谱写美好的青春华章。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);">经济管理学院里的教室总是窗明几净，桌椅整齐，这离不开</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">经管er</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);">的辛勤劳动，Ta们满怀热血，通过劳动铸就青春底色。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELIJuEGz6kkmUCypoTSlibr7vsPkDCfLpXK7rmeZpq54IubXbZttWWFiawh6ZaYqOksLia5INUZ1Hib1Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="195" height="126" style="width: 195px; height: 126px;"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);">当劳动碰上青团——</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;">经管er</span></strong><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);">把勤劳当做馅，把幸福当做是皮。一粒青团，饱含了自食其力的人物精神；四方食事，蕴藏了勤劳俭朴的安中烟火。人生在勤，不索何获。就让我们从小事做起，从一粒青团做起，先劳后得，尽享其乐！</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 229);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELIJuEGz6kkmUCypoTSlibr7xUh5ib5KDogRVK9jnLoUL11m7YgibP3tpx49n3iaDicJgcsZ8EHhz36FGg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="203" height="128" style="width: 203px; height: 128px;"/></span></span></p>